Summary:        Load config files of various types
Version:        0.30
Release:        7%{?dist}
License:        GPL+ or Artistic
Group:          Development/Libraries
Source0:        http://search.cpan.org/CPAN/authors/id/B/BR/BRICAS/Catalyst-Plugin-ConfigLoader-%{version}.tar.gz 
